node.text: I am in the process of searching for my first home and it has been a competitive process, so I sat down with @meredithrealestate to ask questions and get some clarity on how to stay encouraged in this market! Thankful for @bhhscalifornia for their help on this exciting journey!! I used this cover photo to manifest my dream home! #findyourperfect

☺️🎄❤️

node.text: This is the first year in a while that we aren’t on a trip or together on your birthday and I felt so emotional going through all of our photos and videos and all the places we have been! I love you so much and I’m so thankful for your friendship! Can’t wait for our next adventure! ❤️

node.text:
This song is like therapy every time. 
Lately I would describe how I’m feeling in life as being in the in between. It’s like being in the shallow water and you’re not ready to go back and get out of the water, but you’re not ready to go deeper because you haven’t been in the deep and it’s scary (🦈). Anyways, it can be uncomfortable and if you’re in the in between as well, you’re not alone. ❤️

node.text:
My cozy sanctuary ☺️
What is your favorite room in your home? 
.
I just got my shades installed yesterday and now my room gets so dark! Very exciting. Also have the fire place on and a cozy storm on the TV even though it’s hot and sunny outside- I can pretend. 🙇🏻‍♀️

node.text:
Phoebe @ the beach: a series.
This little chicken girl has really been there for me recently during some hard days. It’s so weird how our animals can give so much emotional comfort to us when we hurt. It makes me want to cry. 🥺
